{"word":"σφωέ","slug":"σφωέ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n101785\" key=\"sfwe/\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σφωέ</orth>, dual nom. and acc. of the Pron. of <per opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"per\">3rd pers.</per>, of which the gen. sg. and nom. pl. are <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὗ, σφεῖς</foreign> (qq. v.); dat. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σφωΐν</foreign>:—<sense id=\"n101785.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">they two, both of them</tr_>, only masc. and fem., and always enclit., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.8</biblScope></bibl>, al.; strengthd., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σφωΐν ἀμφοτέροιιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:20:327\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.327</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>:—the form <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σφώ</foreign> is only found in post-Homeric <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram></gramGrp>, as <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0239.tlg002:9:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Antim.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.11</biblScope> </bibl> (in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:531\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.531</biblScope> </bibl> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σφω᾽ Αἴαντε</foreign> is the best reading, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0082.tlg001:88:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.D.\">A.D.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pron.\">Pron.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">88.24</biblScope></bibl>, Hdn.Gr.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0082.tlg001:2:72\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.72</biblScope> </bibl>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}